raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: djangorestframework_simplejwt
  version: 5.5.0

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/djangorestframework_simplejwt-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 474a1b737067e6462b3609627a392d13a4da8a08b1f0574104ac6d7b1406f90e

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  host:
    - python ${{ python_min }}.*
    - setuptools-scm
    - setuptools
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - django >=4.2
    - djangorestframework >=3.14
    - pyjwt >=1.7.1,<2.10.0

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - rest_framework_simplejwt
      pip_check: true
      python_version: ${{ python_min }}

about:
  summary: A minimal JSON Web Token authentication plugin for Django REST Framework
  license: MIT AND BSD-2-Clause
  license_file:
    - LICENSE.txt
    - licenses/LICENSE-django-rest-framework.md
    - licenses/LICENSE-django-rest-framework-jwt
  homepage: https://github.com/jazzband/djangorestframework-simplejwt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
    - riggggo
    - janjagusch
